name: Fiber
description: Tangled treasures from island grass.

name: Thornmelons
description: Prickly fruits for a poke-filled harvest. Watch out for thorny surprises!

name: Quarkberries
description: Sweet and peculiar, just like this place.

name: Seaweed Fiber
description: Seashore secret for crafting needs.

description: Iron with a touch of kelp magic.

name: Sea Urchin Spines
description: Prickly prizes from deep-sea urchins.

description: A testament to conquering the sea's mightiest.

description: From the depths of the cave comes this mysterious artifact. Is it a remnant of an ancient civilization or something else?

name: Sea Meat
description: Savory bounty from the ocean's creatures.

name: Spear
description: The perfect tool for when you want to stab something, but don't want to get too close.
